Support the development of MBSC DEFI LLC DBA: MBSC DEFI

MBSC DEFI is currently a branch of MBSC Global a GPU Crypto Mining, USG Telecommunications Contractor, and industry leader in integrating Blockchain technology with DoD Enterprise Solutions. The MBSC DEFI Division has matured significantly, and our corporate vision requires us to incorporate MBSC DEFI from an internal branch to fully functioning corporate body (Corporation). Thus, our intent is to drive funds accrued from NFT sales to finance MBSC DEFI LLC "MBSC DEFI" in 2023, a wholly owned subsidiary of MBSC Global LLC. Participants will hold real voting membership rights. 

Owners of this NFT ($MBSC) will be the only authorized votes for MBSC DEFI Projects.

Members Who Purchase 10 $MBSC NFT's will also receive quarterly distributions in MBSC DEFI (MBSC) respective to their ownership % of $MBSC.
